casebody.data:
J. Stanford LIFSEY, Esq., Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
The BANK OF TAMPA, et al., Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-1766 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. May 24, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Petitioner's petition for writ of prohibition is denied.

Bank of Tampa's motion for determination that it is not a respondent or to dismiss the petition as to Bank of Tampa is denied as moot.

NORTHCUTT, SALARIO, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
